title: Songsterr v1.39.15
description:
Songsterr is a tab app with instant access to 400,000 high quality guitar, bass and drum tabs. 

When you buy the app, you get unlimited lifetime access to all the tabs.

FEATURES

Tabs
- Huge catalogue of accurate tabs from Songsterr.com. Unlimited instant access to 400,000 tabs.
- High transcription quality. There is only one version of tab per song.
- Legality. Music creators get paid.

Tab Player
- Realistic Guitar Engine. Learn and play along with Songsterr.
- Multiple Instruments. Most songs have tabs for individual instruments (guitar, bass, drums, vocal, etc).
- Half Speed. Slow down tab playback to learn difficult parts.
- Offline Mode. View and playback previously opened tabs offline.
- Count in. Gives you time to prepare yourself for playing after tapping Play.
- Solo. Hear just the instrument you are learning.

Navigation
- History. Instantly access tabs you viewed recently.
- Favorites. Quickly access your favorite tabs.

What's New:

* 1.39.15
- minor bugfixes & ui imrovements.
- add preference to enable / disable cursor movement smoothing to settings on tab screen.
